house Disney Magazine Philippines'') is an educational magazine published in the [[Philippines]] by [[Summit Media]] in collaboration with [[The Walt Disney Company|The Walt Disney Company Southeast Asia]].\n\n==Notes==\n{{reflist|group=note}}\n\n==References==\n<references />\n\n{{Disney Channel}}\n\n[[Category:Disney Junior|Asia]]\n[[Category:Children's television channels in the Asia Pacific]]\n[[Category:Commercial-free television networks]]\n[[Category:Television programming blocks in Asia]]\n[[Category:Television channels and stations established in 2004]]\n[[Category:Media in Southeast Asia]]\n[[Category:English-language television stations]]\n[[Category:Television channel articles with incorrect naming style]]\n", "name_user": "TheGreatSG'rean", "label": "safe", "comment": "Standarised with other Disney pages.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disney_Junior_(Asian_TV_channel)"}
